<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-8 mx-auto">
        <div class="card shadow">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h3 class="card-title text-center mb-4">Welcome to the Gray Areas of Human Judgment</h3>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Step into scenarios that will test your moral compass. Face heart-wrenching dilemmas 
                    that have puzzled philosophers for centuries, and discover how your decisions compare 
                    with others around the world.
                </p>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Every choice reveals something about your ethical framework. Will you prioritize the 
                    greatest good for the greatest number? Do intentions matter more than outcomes? 
                    <strong>Some choices will haunt you forever.</strong>
                </p>
                <div class="text-center mt-4">
                    <form method="post" asp-page-handler="Start">
                        <label for="UserName" class="form-label">Enter your name or nickname to begin:</label>
                         <input type="text" id="UserName" name="UserName" class="form-control w-50 mx-auto mb-3" placeholder="Your name" required />
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-start btn-lg"> Start with The Trolley Problem</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-5">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h4> Think Deeply</h4>
            <p>Explore classic thought experiments that challenge your moral intuitions.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h4> Compare Responses</h4>
            <p>See how your choices align with others facing the same moral crossroads.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h4> Learn Ethics</h4>
            <p>Discover the philosophical frameworks behind moral decision-making.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
